@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> Rejected
Rejected --> Delivered : submit
Delivered --> Completed : review
Delivered : entry / log author
Completed --> Created : cancel
Created --> Archived : cancel
Created : entry / log author
Archived --> Closed : process
Closed --> [*]
@enduml